Create and Share an App from the Analytics for Communications - Consumer Template

Create an app from the Analytics for Communications - Consumer template, available in Developer Edition and Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

To create: 
- CRM Analytics Plus Admin permission set
To use:
- CRM Analytics Plus User permission set

Navigate to CRM Analytics Studio.
Click Create, then select App.
Select Analytics for Communications - Consumer, then click Continue.
Take a quick look at the preview page, then click Continue to open the configuration wizard.

The next page asks you to select the dataset that has the payment and usage data. Click Looks good, next.
Name your app, then click Create.

View the status of the app creation on the next screen. The process takes a minute or two. After itâ€™s complete, refresh the page to see your app.

Share the app with your users by inviting them in CRM Analytics Studio.
